  "Description": {
    "English": "An exclusive <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Starship</span> with a spacious cargo hold, and pre-fitted with illegally modified <span class=\"name name-technology\">Deflector Shields</span>.<br><br><span class=\"name name-stellar\">Claim</span> this ship to add it to your collection, or <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Exchange</span> it with your current ship. While on a planet, summon ships from the Quick Menu (<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>).",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一艘拥有大容量货仓的专属<span class=\"name name-stellar\">飞船</span>，预装有非法改造版<span class=\"name name-technology\">偏导护盾</span>。<br><br><span class=\"name name-stellar\">收取</span>这艘飞船，将它加入你的收藏，或与你现在的飞船<span class=\"name name-stellar\">交换</span>。在行星上时，使用快捷菜单（<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>）召唤飞船。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "一艘特殊<span class=\"name name-stellar\">太空船</span>，配備寬裕的貨艙，而且預裝了非法改造的<span class=\"name name-technology\">反射防護罩</span>。<br><br><span class=\"name name-stellar\">領取</span>這艘船加入你的收藏，或是與目前太空船<span class=\"name name-stellar\">交換</span>。在星球上時，利用快捷選單 (<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>) 召喚太空船。"
  },
